If the integration being ARCHIVED is tagged as "HEAD", the tag is removed from this snapshot and set to the previous non-ARCHIVED snapshot. The PUBLISH_REQUESTED, DUE_FOR_DELETION tags are removed too. This RPC throws an exception if the version being archived is DRAFT, and if the `locked_by` user is not the same as the user performing the Archive.
